OL,3,CMan jailed for murdering his neighbour
OL,4,Cafter dispute over a paintbrush
OL,6,FA man from Huddersfield has been
OL,7,Fjailed for a minimum of 17 years for
OL,8,Fthe murder of a pensioner who he
OL,9,Fviolently attacked in his own home.
OL,11,FDavid Hill, of South Cross Road in
OL,12,FHuddersfield, was first arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of assault following an
OL,14,Fincident on 21 February 2023 when he
OL,15,Fattacked 77-year-old Kurt Giwisser. He
OL,16,Fwas later arrested on suspicion or
OL,17,Fmurder.
