OL,3,CMan jailed for murdering his neighbour
OL,4,Cafter dispute over a paintbrush
OL,6,FHill, who was drunk at the time,
OL,7,Fbanged on Mr Giwisser's patio door
OL,8,Fand, in fear he would smash it, Mr
OL,9,FGiwisser opened it.
OL,11,FHill then forced his way in and
OL,12,Fattacked Mr Giwisser by punching and
OL,13,Fkicking him. He also threatened to
OL,14,Fkill him.
OL,16,FLeeds Crown Court heard Hill stopped
OL,17,Fthe attack when Mr Giwisser begged him
OL,18,Fto and told him his age.
