OL,3,CMan jailed for murdering his neighbour
OL,4,Cafter dispute over a paintbrush
OL,6,FThe court heard that Hill, who is 57,
OL,7,Fhad held a grudge against his
OL,8,Fneighbour after he returned a
OL,9,Fpaintbrush to him and he did not like
OL,10,Fthe state of it.
OL,12,FMr Giwisser was taken to hospital for
OL,13,Ftreatment for head injuries. A few
OL,14,Fdays later he lost consciousness and
OL,15,FCT scans showed blood on his brain.
OL,17,FHis health declined and Mr Giwisser
OL,18,Fdied in April 2023.
