OL,3,CMan jailed for murdering his neighbour
OL,4,Cafter dispute over a paintbrush
OL,6,FThe court heard that following surgery
OL,7,Fand complications, Mr Giwisser's
OL,8,Fdaughters had to make the decision to
OL,9,Fturn off his life support.
OL,11,FHill has been given a life sentence
OL,12,Fwith a minimum term of 17 years behind
OL,13,Fbars.
OL,15,FJudge Robin Mairs told Hill: "In the
OL,16,Ffinal months, your attack robbed (Mr
OL,17,FGiwisser) of the security of his
OL,18,Fbeloved home. He became terrified of
OL,19,Fyou and reclusive, closing the
OL,20,Fcurtains.
