OL,6,F"There has been no word of remorse or
OL,7,Fcontrition from you or recognition for
OL,8,Fthe magnitude of what you have done
OL,9,Fand the grief you have caused."
OL,11,FThe court heard Hill had previous
OL,12,Fconvictions on his record as a youth
OL,13,Ffor burglary and that he went on to
OL,14,Fcommit arson and harassment. In 2020,
OL,15,Fhe was convicted of making indecent
OL,16,Fphotographs and pseudo-photographs of
OL,17,Fchildren.
